('> Remove it. Apple will reject apps that request permissions speculatively. Only request Bluetooth when the user first attempts a Bluetooth-dependent ', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'and ensure that action is reachable by the reviewer without a paid account.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
