('> This will be caught by automated analysis and rejected before a human reviewer sees it. Replace with the public UIKit animation APIs (`UIViewPropert', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', '`UIView.animate`). Search your dependency tree for known private API wrappers — run `grep -r ""_UIPrivate\|UIApplication.*openURL"" .` in your project to surface obvious calls.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('> All three are public', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'documented frameworks. No private API risk here. Run `nm -u YourApp.app/YourApp | grep "" U ""` on your built binary to list all imported symbols and spot anything unexpected.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('**What Apple checks:** Reviewers test on real devices running the minimum OS version declared in your build. A crash on launch', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'a black screen for more than a few seconds', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('**What Apple checks:** If an app requires account creation before the user can see any functionality', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'reviewers will flag it. Apple''s rule: users must be able to experience the core value of the app before being asked to register.', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
('**What Apple checks:** Since June 2022', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'any app that allows account creation must also allow account deletion from within the app. A mailto link', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
