('**What Apple checks:** If any feature requires authentication', 'From awesome-chatgpt-prompts community collection', 'the reviewer must be able to access it. If they cannot', 'chatgpt', 1, ARRAY['community', 'chatgpt', 'prompts'], 'General use'),
